#!/usr/bin/env bash

$PAGER <<-'EOF'

https://wiki.termux.com/wiki/Touch_Keyboard

Volume Up:

    E   → Escape
    T   → Tab
    1-9 → F1-F9
    0   → F10
    B   → Alt+b
    F   → Alt+f
    X   → Alt+x
    W   → Up
    A   → Left
    S   → Down
    D   → Right
    L   → | (pipe)
    H   → ~ (tilde)
    U   → _ (underscore)
    P   → Page Up
    N   → Page Down
    .   → Ctrl+\ (SIGQUIT)
    V   → Volume control
    Q/K → Toggle toolbar

Volume Down → Ctrl

--------------------------------------------------

https://wiki.termux.com/wiki/Hardware_Keyboard

Ctrl+Alt:

    C   → Create new session
    R   → Rename current session
    M   → Show menu
    U   → Select URL
    V   → Paste
    +/- → Adjust text size
    1-9 → Go to numbered session
    K   → Enable/Disable soft keyboard

    Up (or P)   → Previous session
    Down (or N) → Next session
    Right       → Open drawer
    Left        → Close drawer

EOF
